458
00:38:51,038 --> 00:38:52,208
Aku kesal memikirkan itu.

459
00:38:53,748 --> 00:38:56,088
"Sulit kupercaya
cinta pertamanya begitu cantik."

460
00:38:56,588 --> 00:38:58,338
Aku cemburu memikirkan itu.

461
00:38:59,928 --> 00:39:02,218
"Aku penasaran seperti apa Pak Noh
saat berusia 21 tahun.

462
00:39:03,348 --> 00:39:06,058
